Second Department,

January, 1951.

(January 4, 1951.) In the Matter of the Application of Hortensia L. Quintana for a Writ of Habeas Corpus to Bring up Priscilla M. H. Quintana, an Infant. The People of the State of New York ex rel. Hortensia L. Quintana, Respondent, against Raul L. Quintana, Appellant.

Order sustaining writ of habeas corpus affirmed, without costs. No opinion. Carswell, Acting P. J., Johnston, Adel, Sneed and Wenzel, JJ., concur.
